			I'm currently looking for new opportunities to build exciting products. Whether you have a question, a project idea, or
			just want to say hi, I'll try my best to get back to you!
		</p>

		<a href="mailto:hammadharquil@gmail.com" class="retro-contact-primary">
			<h3>Email</h3>
			<p>hammadharquil@gmail.com</p>
		</a>

		<div class="retro-contact-grid">
			<a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/hammadharquil/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="retro-contact-card">
				LinkedIn
			</a>
			<a href="https://twitter.com/elitepsd" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="retro-contact-card">Twitter / X</a>
			<a href="https://github.com/hammvdh" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="retro-contact-card">GitHub</a>
			<a href="https://instagram.com/hammvdh" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="retro-contact-card">Instagram</a>
